<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p>
1: I make a staff of power to get the spell power flag.  (ego adding can do that, artifact making can't) 
</p>
<p>
2: artifact it, and raise pval to say 200 at no cost because artifact creation doesn't have a price for this flag. 
</p>
<p>
3: I add curse no drop or some inexpensive flag (this is necessary because pval can't be improved without adding a flag). 
</p>
<p>
4: I enjoy my "free" 200 levels of spell power hack. This is sweet revenge for not adding spell power to artifact creation, which annoyed me to no end! 
</p>
<p>
Suggested quick fix: add a cost for raising the pval, even in absence of all flags. 
</p>
<p>
Long term fix: wait for version 3.0 where spell power is probably implemented 
</p>
